[25/11/2017 15:41:59] <font color="#ffffff">Ukiyo.</font>
[25/11/2017 15:41:59] <font color="#00ff00">No es correcto.</font>
[25/11/2017 15:42:01] <font color="#00ff00">¿Por dónde se propaga</font>
